name: POLER Rucksack / green camo
description:
When did backpacks get so complicated? The Rucksack is a classic old school design that looks as good now as it did 30 years ago. It comes with removable side pouches that strap to the sides for toiletries, a water bottle or other accessories. Take the pouches off and use them as internal organizers. Once they are off, the bag is much slimmer and is a great size for daily use at school or the office. It has a padded internal laptop sleeve that fits most 15" laptops to seal the deal.

The Rucksacks dimensions are 12 X 5 X 18 with a total carrying capacity of 28.6 liters. The main compartment comes in at 21.6 liters, the two side bags are at 2.3 each, and the top bag fits 2.4 liters.

This is an everyday pack, not an expedition pack, It's not meant for loads over 20lbs, and the side pouches aren't meant to carry heavy stuff either. They work great for a water bottle or a magic tarpit, don't load them down with anything heavier than that.

-1000D Campdura body fabric and are lined with 420D nylon

-Nylon webbing is seatbelt webbing, super high tensile strength

-Our Cyclops logo is now embossed on all our snaps. All our leather pull tabs also have Camp Vibes embossed into them

-Internal padded Laptop sleeve to keep your laptop safe

categories.name: B A C K P A C K

name: POLER Napsack / orange
description:
The Napsack has zippers at the shoulders, so you can stick your arms out, and a cinch at the bottom so that you can open it up and stick your legs out. Hike it up to your waist, cinch it, and wear it like a puffy coat around the campfire, and then crawl right back into your tent without ever having to leave the warmth of your bag.

Perfect for summer trips, couch surfing, music festivals, jumping into after snowboarding, surfing or any other activity that bring your core temp down. Its not too hot for inside and is awesome for wearing around the house in the winter.

The chest pocket fits a phone and has a pass through hole for your headphones to run internally, and it has pockets like a puffy jacket.

Size LARGE

categories.name: R E C Y C L E D

name: Skateboard cutting board
description:
Cutting board / serving tray made from recycled skateboard decks. 
Each cutting board keeps three broken skateboards from entering the landfill. The boards are de-gripped and cut into strips. Each strip is sanded and glued together with a food safe, water based glue and pressed overnight to create a one of a kind cutting board. They work equally well as a cheese tray or serving platter.
Each board is hand sanded, and finished with boiled linseed oil.

Care instructions: Hand wash with warm soap and water, do not put in dishwasher, or leave submerged in water. (it is made from wood after all)

. approximate dimensions are 12" x 8" x .75"
. colors vary due to available inventory
. message me if you have a color preference

categories.name: R E C Y C L E D

name: Skateboard Bottle Opener / layers
description:
It all starts with a broken skateboard.  The decks are cut into slices, glued together using a water based wood adhesive, and pressed overnight to achieve a layered block of wood.  Slices are then cut out of the block and then the pattern is cut out.  These are all hand cut and finished, and of course, they work great for opening your favorite beverage.

*colors may vary, please specify if you have a certain color preference.

categories.name: R E C Y C L E D

name: Skateboard drink coaster / round
description:
The round drink coasters are made from the part of the skateboard that is left over from making the other items in our store, the nose and the tail. Each piece is cut and sanded by hand. Several coats of a clear and protective enamel are applied after finishing. This seals the coaster and brings out the colors in each layer. A layer of cork is applied to keep the coaster from sliding, and from scuffing up your furniture. (the scratches and scuffs that come from skateboarding make each coaster unique, embrace their uniqueness)

. approximate size is 3 1/2" x 1/2" 
. listing is for a set of 4
. colors will vary

more info: http://www.s3bs.com/recycles/

name: Skateboard Bottle Opener / standard
description:
Recycled from broken skateboard decks.
All of the keychain bottle openers are hand selected, hand cut (with a bandsaw), and sanded by hand.  In the spirit of re-using and recycling, we use the grip tape from the broken boards to sand the keychains.   The bottle openers then receive a protective clear coat to keep the colors vibrant.

We make each one by hand, so there are slight differences and variances that make each one unique and totally awesome.   They are great for opening bottles too.

* colors may vary

categories.name: R E C Y C L E D

name: Skateboard Drink Coaster / square
description:
Each broken deck is de-gripped and cut into thin strips. These strips are then sanded, glued and placed in a press for several hours. The final product is hand sanded, then a clear coat is applied to keep it from staining and to bring out the colors of each veneer. The underside of each coaster is lined with cork so it won't scratch.   

. colors may vary slightly
. finished size is roughly 3.25" x 3.25" by .25" thick 
. listing is for one (1) coaster

"The original skateboard drink coasters"

description:
The mini bottle opener is made from broken skateboards that we collect from our retail store. They are produced one at a time in the back of our shop. Each piece is sanded and finished by hand. The bottle openers then receive a clear protective enamel finish. (this enhances the veneer colors)

We make each one by hand, so there are slight differences and variances that make each one unique and totally awesome. They are great for opening bottles too.

. size is approximately 2" x 1"
. colors may vary
